<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>A <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1Manager">Manager</link> is a container for items with a common base class.</para>

<para>A <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1Manager">Manager</link> is is a subclass of <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1ParamComposite">ParamComposite</link> that manages a list of subclasses of a base class, which it creates using an associated <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1Factory">Factory</link>. </para>
